\par }{\f100\fs22\insrsid5310506 Evrim teorisi, canl\'fdlar\'fdn varl\'fd\'f0\'fdn\'fd ve k\'f6kenini tesad\'fcflerle a\'e7\'fdklayabilmek amac\'fdyla \'e7e\'feitli ger\'e7ek d\'fd\'fe\'fd tahminler ve varsay\'fdmlar, hayal mahsul\'fc senaryolar \'fc
