\par }{\f0\fs22\lang1031\langfe1055\langnp1031\insrsid5310506 A}{\f100\fs22\lang1031\langfe1055\langnp1031\insrsid5310506 ncak bu durumda evrenin her yerinde apa\'e7\'fdk g\'f6r\'fcnen "yarat\'fdlm\'fd\'fel\'fdk" \'f6zelli\'f0ini gizlemek, evrenin ve canl\'fd
